Dungeon rats are a type of rat found in caves, sewers, and dungeons underneath the city of Ardougne. They are fairly easy foes to defeat and don't give very much experience on death. As such, training on them is not recommended.

A group of them play a key role in the Clock Tower quest in which the player poisons their food trough. This causes the rats to attempt to escape by chewing away a railing, allowing the player to grab the white cog.
